Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Alcohol - Official Teaser | Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika Nm  | Meher Tej | S Naga Vamsi
snippet.description:
Watch Alcohol - Official Teaser | Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika Nm  | Meher Tej | S Naga Vamsi 

Alcohol is a Telugu feature film starring Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika NM, Satya, and an ensemble cast. Directed by Meher Tej, the film features music by Ghibran, background score by Chaitan Bharadwaj, cinematography by Jiju Sunny, and editing by Niranjan Devaramane.

Produced by Suryadevara Naga Vamsi and Sai Soujanya under Sithara Entertainments and Fortune Four Cinemas, the film is presented by Srikara Studios.

Cast: Allari Naresh, Ruhani Sharma, Niharika NM, Satya, Girish Kulkarni, Harshavardhan, Chaitanya Krishna, Ravindra Vijay, Raghu Babu, Venkatesh Kakumanu, Kireeti, Hariteja, Surya Bhagavan Das, Flora Jacob

snippet.title: LOKAH CHAPTER 1: CHANDRA Official Teaser & Trailer Reaction! | Kalyani Priyadarshan | Naslen
snippet.description:
Achara & Michael react to the teaser and trailer of Lokah, a visually stunning and emotionally charged epic that blends mythology, action, and heart. From breathtaking visuals to an atmosphere steeped in culture and mystery, Lokah promises a cinematic ride that feels both grand and deeply personal. Our reactions? Intrigued, blown away, and eager to see how this world unfolds on the big screen
____________________

Thank you to our Jamazing Patron: Krishna Venkataraman!

Be a patron for CineDesi and support more videos like this!

Welcome to the TEZ FFMIC League Stage!

18 of India's elite teams have made it through, but only the best will survive. They will face the ultimate test of skill across two demanding modes to forge their legacy.

The action kicks off TOMORROW!

üì∫ Tune in live for every intense showdown:

Battle Royale:
üìÖ Week 1: Aug 22, 23, 24
üìÖ Week 2: Aug 29, 30, 31
üìÖ Week 3: Sep 6, 7
üìÖ Week 4: Sep 13, 14

Clash Squad:
üìÖ Week 1: Sep 5
üìÖ Week 2: Sep 12

The fight for the crown continues. Who are you rooting for?
#TEZ #FFMIC #FFM #Booyah

snippet.title: Ram Jaane (Music Video) Anu Malik | Shahrukh Khan, Juhi Chawla | Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam|Hindi song
snippet.description:
‚ÄúRam Jaane‚Äù is the bold and unforgettable title track from the 1995 Bollywood action-drama Ram Jaane, sung by Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam and composed by Anu Malik. The song captures the gritty, rebellious spirit of the film‚Äôs lead character, played by Shah Rukh Khan, whose very name ‚Äî Ram Jaane (meaning ‚ÄúGod knows‚Äù) ‚Äî becomes a powerful identity statement.

#RamJaane #ShahRukhKhan #JuhiChawla #UditNarayan #AlkaYagnik #SonuNigam #AnuMalik #BollywoodClassics #SRKMovies #BollywoodAction #HindiMovieSongs #RamJaaneSong #BollywoodHits #EvergreenBollywood #SRKFans #BollywoodSoundtrack #ClassicSRK #IndianCinema #BollywoodAnthems #BollywoodThrowback #DesiVibes

Singer: Udit Narayan, Alka Yagnik, Sonu Nigam
Music: Anu Malik
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Ram Jaane

Director: Rajiv Mehra
Producer: Parvesh Mehra
Label: Universal Music India

Ram jaane, ram jaane

Ram jaane, ram jaane

‚ô™

Jo jhooth-sach ko pahachaanata hai

‚ô™

snippet.description:
Saiyaara (1980) Ft. Kishore Kumar full song (Old version) Old is Gold with a New Voice!

The full version is finally here! We converted the vocals sung amazingly by RJ Kisna into kishore da's voice using AI, and I produced the retro background music, let me know if ya'll want a breakdown of how I do these retro versions! 




üåç Follow me here for more fun and behind the scenes:
Instagram - 
@anshuman.sharma1 |   / anshuman.sharma1  
Twitter - @anshumonsharma |   / anshumonsharma  
Facebook - @anshuman.sharma111 |   / anshuman.sharma1  

Saiyaara (1980) ‚Äì Kishore Kumar's Saiyaara Full Song 
Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Whether you're a lifelong Kishore fan or discovering his magic for the first time, this song is a journey into the past that you don't want to mi

Credit goes to _Rakesh Sutradhar üôè

[Verse 1]
Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Tu paas hai mere paas hai aise
Mera koi ehsaas hai jaise

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Verse 2]
Beetey lamhon se duniya basa loon
Main toh tere aansuon ka bana hoon

Meri hansi mein teri sadaayein
Teri kahaani khud ko sunaaun

Yaadon ke taare, yaadon ke taare tootenge kaise
Mere hain jo woh roothenge kaise

Beetey dinon ki kholi kitaabein
Guzre palon ko kaise bhula dein

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Baaton mein teri main raatein bitaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

[Chorus Repeat]
Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi
Tere bina tab kuch na rahenge

[Outro]
Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

Re Dedyu Sansa Ki Qurbani 
Du Ya Tere Pe Vaar Jawani 
Bhaiya Khatar Bhai Marjya

Teri Khatar Naash Karange 
Dil Mei Tere Vaas Karange 
Sedhaniya Ke Baas Dharange...

Re Na Jaan Kati Dariye 
Jukar Duryodhan Ki Khatar
Ran Mei Karan Khadya Tha Adke
Nyuhi Teri Khater Khada Yaar Tera
Chinta Naa Kariye ‚Ä¶.
Saamhi Arjun Ho Ya Koi Uste bhi bada Yodha Je na Mila Khaak Mei Aaya Toh Fer Baat Kariye ..

Re Junse Chale Khilafat Mei Na Unene Bilkul Chalan Da
Agle Kare baat Maran ki 
Hum Na Baal Bhi Hallan Da
Un Ne Andaza Bhi Konya Mahara Jeen Ka Fayda Ke
Mahre Hote Haath Gerde Mahara Jeen Ka Fayda Ke ..
Re 
Unki Teere Laash Naale Mei 
Beshak Karde Fon Saale Nei
Jindgi Di Uppar Aale Nei
Jeeke Suthri Dhaal Mariye... 

Jyukar Duryodhan Ki Khatar 
Ran Mei Karan Khada Tha Aadke 
Nyue Teri Khatar Khada yaar Tera
Chinta na kariye ‚Ä¶
Re Saamhi Arjun Ho Ya Koi Uste Bhi Bada Yodha Je Na Mila Khaak Mei Aaya Mere Te Fer Baat Kariye ..

Jo Asal Mard Mei Khubi Wo Mahare Saari Pawengi 
Ghaate Mei Khoon Ho Chae Na Howe Par Khudari Pawegi..
Amar Mei Nu Toh Bojh S Thoda Par Baat Bhari Pawegi... Karnawliya Lakh Bura Par Na Gadari Pawegi
Aare Hum Issi Baat Te Chaegye Jiste Lage To Bs Lagye Humto Yaari Tod Nibhaya Gaye Tu Bi Baat Te Na Firye

Jyukar Duryodhan Ki Khatar 
Ran Mei Karan Khada Tha Aadke 
Nyue Teri Khatar Khada yaar Tera
Chinta na kariye
Re Saamhi Arjun Ho Ya Koi Uste Bhi Bada Yodha Je Na Mila Khaak Mei Aaya Mere Te Fer Baat Kariye
